4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, with no prior knowledge required. The 16-week program includes three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will build a foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course also covers risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Instruction is available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop